{"article_id":"WIlU6H0uiFkwFL1e","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump faces legal challenges to his decision","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"to use emergency powers","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to build a wall on the US border with Mexico .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"California and New York said","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"they would take legal action","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"to challenge his move","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"to bypass Congress","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"and secure funding for the project .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Building the wall was a key pledge of Mr Trump 's campaign .","depth":3},{"id":9,"text":"Democrats said","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"it was a `` gross abuse of power ''","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"and vowed to contest it","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"`` using every remedy available '' .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"On Friday , Mr Trump signed the emergency declaration along with a spending bill","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"aimed at preventing a repeat of a recent government shutdown .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"Declaring an emergency could give him access to billions of dollars .","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"Mr Trump announced the plan","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"after Congress refused funding for the wall .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Within hours , the first legal challenge against the declaration of national emergency was launched .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"A liberal advocacy group , Public Citizen , sued on behalf of a nature reserve and three Texas landowners","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"who have been told","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"the wall may be constructed on their properties .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Governor Gavin Newsom of California dismissed the president 's decision as `` political theatre '' .","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"`` He 's been embarrassed ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"and his base needs to be fed , ''","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"`` Fortunately , Donald Trump is not the last word .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"The courts will be the last word , ''","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"he added .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"New York state 's Democratic attorney general , Letitia James , said","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"the state would not `` stand for this abuse of power","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"and will fight back with every legal tool at our disposal . ''","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"The American Civil Liberties Union","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"( ACLU )","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"it would file a lawsuit in the coming days","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"to curb `` this blatantly illegal executive action '' .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"On Friday the two most senior Democrats","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"- House of Representatives Speaker Nancy Pelosi and Senate Democrat leader Chuck Schumer -","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"they would challenge the `` power grab by a disappointed president '' in Congress and in the courts .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Ms Pelosi also seized on a remark by Mr Trump in response to a question from a reporter ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"in which he said","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"he `` did n't need to do this '' .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"Analysts suggest","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"that this remark could undermine Mr Trump 's case","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that the country is facing an emergency .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Making the announcement in the White House Rose Garden ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"the president said","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"the emergency would allow him to get almost $ 8bn for the wall .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"This is still considerably short of the estimated $ 23bn cost of the wall along almost 2,000 miles","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"( 3,200km )","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"of border .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"Mr Trump accepted","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"that he would be sued for the move ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"and predicted","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"that the emergency order would lead to legal action","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"which was likely to end up in the Supreme Court .","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"`` We 're going to confront the national security crisis on our southern border , ''","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"Later , Mick Mulvaney , the acting White House chief of staff , told reporters","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"that Mr Trump 's move `` creates zero precedent '' .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"`` This is authority","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"given to the president in law already .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"It 's not as if he just did n't get what he wanted","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"so he 's waving a magic wand","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"and taking a bunch of money , ''","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"The trouble with going nuclear is there is fall-out .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"This has been presented as a predictably partisan issue .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"On one side of the wall , Republicans ;","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"on the other side Democrats .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"But","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"by going nuclear","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"the president has made it more complicated than that .","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"There are a lot of Republicans","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"- in the Senate and in the House -","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"deeply uneasy about what Mr Trump is doing .","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"Why ?","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"Because the constitutional arrangement of the US is that Congress","depth":17},{"id":80,"text":"- not the president -","depth":17},{"id":81,"text":"controls the purse strings","depth":17},{"id":82,"text":"and allocates funds .","depth":17},{"id":83,"text":"This is a major land grab by the president .","depth":16},{"id":84,"text":"It undermines their position","depth":17},{"id":85,"text":"and sets a very dangerous precedent .","depth":17},{"id":86,"text":"The National Emergencies Act contains a clause","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"that allows Congress to terminate the emergency status","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"if both houses vote for it","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"- and the president does not veto .","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"With a comfortable majority in the House , Democrats could pass such a resolution to the Senate .","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"The Republicans control the Senate ,","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"but a number of Republican senators have been vocal in their unease about the president invoking a national emergency .","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"The dissenting Republicans include 2012 presidential contender and new senator for Utah Mitt Romney , Florida senator Marco Rubio , and the senator from Maine Susan Collins ,","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"who said","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"the move was of `` dubious constitutionality '' .","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"The resolution would however still require Mr Trump 's signature","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"to pass ,","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"allowing him to veto it .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"A supermajority in both houses of Congress is needed","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"to overturn a presidential veto .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"The National Emergencies Act is intended for times of national crisis .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"Mr Trump has claimed","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"that there is a migration crisis at the nation 's southern border","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"- a claim","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"strongly refuted by migration experts .","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"The largest number of illegal migrants","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"settling in the US each year","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"is those","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"who stay in the country","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"after their visas expire .","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"Declaring a national emergency would give the president access to special powers","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"that effectively allow him to bypass the usual political process ,","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"and he would be able to divert money from existing military or disaster relief budgets","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"to pay for the wall .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Emergency declarations by previous presidents have been overwhelmingly used","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"for addressing foreign policy crises","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"- including blocking terrorism-linked entities from accessing funds","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"or prohibiting investment in nations","depth":15},{"id":119,"text":"associated with human rights abuses .","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"On Friday , Mr Mulvaney said","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"the $ 8bn would be made up of :","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"The latter is the biggest amount","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"and the relevant statute allows a president to divert funds for projects","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"that `` require use of the armed forces '' .","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"This is almost certain to bring a legal challenge .","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"A congressional aide told ABC News","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"projects","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"that could be cancelled","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"include constructions at Guantanamo Bay , a military school in Japan and special forces facilities in North Carolina .","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"Poor living conditions for military families have become a concern","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"but a Pentagon spokesman , Bill Speaks , insisted","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"`` military family-housing projects will not be affected '' .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"Trump officials also said","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"that projects","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"affecting force-readiness","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"would not be compromised .","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"Mr Trump said","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"military officials had told him","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"the wall was more important","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"and that what he was told would be cut","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"`` did n't sound too important to me '' .","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":283,"left":154,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":149,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":144,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":0,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":3,"right":147,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":147,"left":4,"right":146,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":5,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":8,"right":152,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":152,"left":9,"right":151,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":10,"right":150,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":162,"right":281,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":162,"left":156,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":155,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":157,"right":160,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":18,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":